Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,title_3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========正文========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸第二天完全恢復了健康
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直游到傍晚 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒有穿小褲褲 句號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到慶典了 因為這個的關係被殿下叫來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶典？

Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說連接9個世界的世界樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以認為其本質就是世界本身的體現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我們能像這樣平安地生活在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全靠了世界樹支撐著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 每年都要舉辦一次感謝世界樹 並藉此狂歡的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶典上公主殿下會…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護這片土地的夢魔王族會作為代表唱歌跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並表現出對世界樹的感謝之意是這的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過從上一代開始主旨稍微發生了一些改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下去年沒有參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年竟然主動說要獻唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶典的本質是為了表示對世界樹的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想殿下是想要向世界樹表示謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年沒有參加的殿下 使她改變心意的是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示 跟世界樹有關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是開始有了身為王族的自覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下是想對撮合自己和直哉先生的世界樹表示感謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…像我這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉先生的謙虛雖是美德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也要分清時間場合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和直哉先生相遇真的非常開心」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道想把殿下的一片真心都否定掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去服侍大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有一半是瞎猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 很那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實蘿黛唱歌跳舞都很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要注意不要在大家面前緊張 保持平常心就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳 妳幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉小褲褲來練膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我泡好茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好H
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz35\move(835,468,623,3,1970,0)\c&HCE9026&\3c&HFFC978&\fs40}調\N教\N中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥 為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您回來的真早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分合身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7759E8&\3c&H5425BE&\fs40\pos(784,287)}調\N教\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7759E8&\3c&H5425BE&\fs40\pos(99,243)}完\N成\N。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛 熟練了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下正式上場時也沒問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛大人 請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會和妳一起練習幫妳打氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴池很大 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次和朋友一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的露天浴池能排進妖魔界百景之一 很有名喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能每天享用這種浴池 太令人羨慕了 蘿黛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉卡醬的衣服好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在故鄉我可不會穿這種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小褲褲也是來到這個國家之後才第一次穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 真空很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我也…妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿緊身褲時也不穿小褲褲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接穿啊 這可需要很大的勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在前幾天第一次嘗試了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張感意外地很暢快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為蜜絲特倫的行為不太健康呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您貴庚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:10:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面的成長每個人都有差別啦 請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢魔族很早熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說母后在我這個年紀已經相當那啥啥啥啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥啥啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平平的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 又不是說越大越好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好像喜歡大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊 我的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡果然要來瓶牛奶呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我祖國的慣例喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我也有在洗完澡後喝一點乳牛魔族牛奶的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳牛魔族現擠的奶中含有使女性發育的特殊營養
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在喝 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說要洗完澡後喝啊 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡後 在血液循環流暢的情況下喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能把營養都傳送到胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿來換的衣物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(1123,162,-222,163,3490,0)\c&H96DBF7&\3c&HDC6360&\fs50\bord4\b2}說起來艾爾芙的奶是絕品來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾芙 請賞些奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要 立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想能長大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點搞不懂 不過看上去好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想再大一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經夠大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下她們好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就會變大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 沒問題的殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是冰的就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要再加把勁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說妳已經夠了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大家快把衣服換上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛 大家在等著了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯 現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 都已經練習過那麼多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖 雖說是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 這個氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人有點興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿著浴衣 就好像在人界一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是從東方的國家流傳過來的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄的又很涼快 真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是晚點就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然到現在才說有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這麼穿真的正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 穿浴衣的時候是不穿的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不僅僅是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟別人穿的浴衣相比 長度相差很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是今年的流行款
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚才來 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會跟愛麗卡在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在那裡碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾妳們了真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣很合身喔 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當…當 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉小褲褲 這不公平喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿浴衣的時候把小褲褲脫掉才是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉這麼說的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小褲褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又說這種多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大家好好享受慶典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家興致正高的時候來打擾真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的那個總是那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這那種事 蘿黛~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿浴衣的樣子也十分漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家正準備好好享受一番呢 你別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來身體也恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次要求跟你決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HEDF9FF&\fs50\pos(757,264)\c&H1100D8&}THE \N複\N仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟哪一方更配得上蘿黛 讓我們重新比試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸才不會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油 直哉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡退縮的話就不是男人了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓那孩子蒙羞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子 弱爆了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉 走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 很帥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不虧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的很完美喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的競爭對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在開始才是真正的勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人已經不在了喔 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 居然逃走了嗎 這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差…差差不多到時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 都已經這個時間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就在這裡看著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把特訓的成果展示出來吧 蘿黛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 直哉帶來的明日葉備用內褲也穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也不能以那種穿著上臺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 給妳這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才呢 在店裡有賣的 所以就買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就跟我的配成一對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞斯塔蘿黛殿下 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好僵硬啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉…明日葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想把今天的事趕快寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡之後開心的事情實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪畫日記都不夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 馬上暑假就結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假結束之後怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前做過植物圖鑑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為是野豌豆結果一摘發現是長額負蝗什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉和公主殿下也會永遠記得這個夏天的回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.29,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたしは今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.42,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ピンク色の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.92,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ストロベリーショート…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.59,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぼくは今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.62,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ももいろの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.93,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苺シャーベット
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.32,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひらひら揺れてる　ハート　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.03,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうほら　重ねよう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:02.96,副本EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指と指絡め
